headline: IFF Launches POWERFRESH ACE 2000 to Enhance Bread Sustainability
summary: International Flavors debuts POWERFRESH ACE 2000, a bread enzyme that boosts softness, extends shelf life and supports bakery sustainability goals.

headline: PPG Gains on Cost Actions and Acquisitions Amid Demand Softness
